# Dependency Security Audit - PISC Project

## Python Dependencies
- fastapi>=0.100.0
- uvicorn[standard]>=0.23.0
- python-dotenv>=1.0.0
- pydantic>=2.0.0
- slowapi>=0.1.9
- openai>=1.0.0

## Security Requirements
- Run `pip audit` or `safety check` regularly
- Use `npm audit` for JavaScript dependencies
- Keep dependencies up to date
- Review security advisories for all transitive dependencies
